{"tid":814430,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《都市》停播　彭慧中宋芝齡姚嘉妮等安排","createTime":"2018-09-11T08:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T01:17:01.000Z","uid":60281,"like":4,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"c13377326ca8fd05eaecc854b70810b73f94cba7","tid":814430,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180911/mobile/bkn-20180911141243978-0911_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180911%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180911141243978-0911_00862_001.html&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=52dc7c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180911/mobile/bkn-20180911141243978-0911_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180911/photo/bkn-20180911141243978-0911_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180911150232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180911%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180911141243978-0911_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180911150232&h=5123bfb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對於無綫長壽節目《都市閒情》將會停播，而無綫高層余詠珊亦表示會改革節目，主持之一的彭慧中回覆東網時說：「我真係睇到網上啲報道先知。（有冇收到通知你會繼續做新節目？）我都係等通知咋，希望繼續有工開。（會唔會覺得可惜？節目有20幾年歷史。）節目真係好深入民心，但如果公司真係有新嘅安排，都係為節目做到最好。」 <br />\n<br />\n而另一位主持姚嘉妮則說：「其實我知道嘅嘢唔多！因為公司都未同我哋講！反而消息都係從報章知道！亦冇收到消息我會冇得做！我諗公司都會好快通知我哋！希望一直支持都市閒情嘅觀眾繼續支持我哋啦！」 <br />\n<br />\n至於另一主持宋芝齡對《都巿閒情》將會停播，她說：「我都係啱啱睇到報道，未知公司有啲咩方向，但節目都係如常拍攝，同平時一樣，我照舊負責星期一、三嘅節目。」"},{"pid":"8b0e982f0272773dee11438bfdd36178e6f65473","tid":814430,"uid":94739,"like":100,"dislike":1,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"廢青無得再睇慧中對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746b3dbab2fb12ebd25cfc404e4bd0c1ed12eec8","tid":814430,"uid":122134,"like":171,"dislike":0,"score":171,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:46:10.000Z","msg":"都市閑情都大結局"},{"pid":"d09f9da368e10391b17fe366fccb5382aaec34da","tid":814430,"uid":33352,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"如果唔係班女，仲邊有人睇"},{"pid":"cc1932c012b0c24d70cf6c4784e7ad092612af7c","tid":814430,"uid":7015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:49:50.000Z","msg":"黃焥瑩煮d餸幾岩後生口味"},{"pid":"77b6c47a6791f26bf6e2a25557529fa977909ced","tid":814430,"uid":106408,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"大王係咪正式收皮？"},{"pid":"0123889829b9c38184d91f348e2ca647aaa7d3d1","tid":814430,"uid":34409,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"77b6c47a6791f26bf6e2a25557529fa977909ced","tid":814430,"uid":106408,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"大王係咪正式收皮？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"大王可以著件馬騮衫繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55394504a197c30bcb8cdeb3e91e8c775bc586aa","tid":814430,"uid":3189,"like":138,"dislike":2,"score":136,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:04:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">女主持成日色誘男主持同男嘉賓</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G6033p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG6033p.jpg&h=4013b06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/02/01/140906_1da8714e59f63a38f07ee650a01e8fc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F02%2F01%2F140906_1da8714e59f63a38f07ee650a01e8fc8.jpg&h=0c7d7b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/06/132926_7